                <div class="viewbox">
                    <div id="circlea1" class="viewing" onclick="a1()"></div><div id="circlea2" class="notviewing" onclick="a2()"></div><div id="circlea3" class="notviewing" onclick="a3()"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>The Hope Empowerment Foundation Uganda is a nonprofit organization founded in the Muguluka Village in the eastern Jinja.
            <p>HEFO-UGANDA works with children and old people to help them get a better future. Through our services and work, we aim to empower women, children, older people, and anyone in need.
            <div class="centerbox"><div class="subheading2">Together, we can make a difference.</div></div>
            <div class="btnbox"><div class="btn2"><a href="https://www.paypal.com/pools/c/8AJ2ehFvLD" target="_blank">donate</a></div></div>
            <p>NOTE: Our bank account opening is delayed while we are still under supervision with the National Organization Board at the district level. After they give us a license and permit, then we will be able to open the bank account. Thank you for your patience.
        </div>
    </div>
<a id="services"></a>
<!--services and activities page-->
    <div id="content2">
        <div class="centerbox">
            <div class="heading2">Services</div>
            <div id="images00"><img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/86792d8a6370717c3ca20edb4b44008d/032630f5358ca3bc-3d/s640x960/081d7a9b1264e0b4ce01e0ba2c69e38dbb13a70f.jpg" height="450px" /></div>
        </div>
        <p>We offer child support to help support children. Pictured above is Mutasa Owen, one of the two children currently benefiting from child support and full sponsorship.</p>
        <p>Donations of any amount can help change a child's life. For example, for $30 a month, your sponsored child gets school fees, rice, and seeds.
        <div class="centerbox"><div id="images01"><img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/f89b2055093428062ba7249be9b07799/50d7bb80f35f9b63-c2/s640x960/519807f7ab6308d62d87322df685ee067d9f68f2.jpg" height="450px" /></div></div>
        <p><div class="subheading2">Pledge for Kasone Joan's birthday.</div>
        <p>Joan is the director of HEFO- UGANDA and is dedicating her birthday this year to fundraise for women empowerment programs under HEFO, including agriculture, motivational speeches, and other programs.
        <p>Your contribution creates an impact and change. Thank you and God bless you!
        <p><div class="subheading2">Education Sponsorship Project</div>
        <p>Project objectives:
            <li>increase access of education to orphans and vulnerable children (OVC)</li>
            <li>increase household's condition through economic empowerment</li>
            <li>livelihood training and micro enterprise development for households</li>
            <li>set up sustainable business to generate income</li>
            <li>develop innovative agriculture demonstrations</li>
            <li>strengthen caregiver groups and VSLAS while supporting community leadership roles</li>
            <li>pay school fees and tuition for orphans and vulnerable children</li>
            <li>provide starter kits and funds for beneficiaries</li>
        <p>HEFO will regularly monitor and supervise the project progress, how basic needs are reached for OVC's homes, monthly reports of the project
        <p>COVID-19 has impacted the world and countless families. Education and literacy, both of which have been great challenges even before the pandemic, have worsened. At HEFO-UGANDA, we are here to try our level best to see communities like Muguluka in eastern Uganda Jinja district and Bulopa in eastern Uganda Kamuli district.
        <div class="slideshow">
            <div class="images">
                <div id="images1"><img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/8634adcda69d8742ae340cf356184aea/50d7bb80f35f9b63-74/s1280x1920/ade03a7d185d899ab486d6310f343e6c6f2f02b4.jpg" /></div>
                <div id="images2"><img src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/0332cd2b2bc3a14050c794a5a84879de/50d7bb80f35f9b63-5c/s640x960/de751fd4b1d6e89232905c195b4e59528cb72242.jpg" /></div>
            </div>
            <div class="viewbox">
                <div id="circles1" class="viewing" onclick="s1()"></div><div id="circles2" class="notviewing" onclick="s2()"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p>So far, we have helped these regions' agriculture for more than 55 beneficiaries, but not every dream can be reached without the help of education in the current generation.
        <p>We expect to help over 200 households to support orphans and vulnerable children.
        <p><div class="subheading2">Teach a Man How to Hunt</div>
        <p>How the project helps beneficiaries:
            <li>teaches them skills so they can earn money</li>
            <li>give them capital through loans which they can refund later</li>
        <p>We need your support, help, prayers, and gifts so that we can reach out to these people with numerous dreams.
        <p>Let's make their dreams shine.
    </div>
